com.google.android.material.motion.runtime

Interface Performer.PlanPerformance

  • Enclosing class:
    Performer

    public static interface Performer.PlanPerformance
    A Performer implements this interface in order to support the Add Plans API.

    A Performer can have logic that is configured by the Plans provided to it.
